query:
-- Contact: Charlotte Holland OV
INSERT INTO contacts (propertyId, name, relationship, flags, createdAt, updatedAt)
SELECT id, 'Charlotte Holland OV', 'Owner', 'Seller', NOW(), NOW()
FROM properties WHERE addressLine1 LIKE '%285 Sw 12th%' AND city = 'Pompano Beach'
ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE name = VALUES(name), updatedAt = NOW();

INSERT INTO contactPhones (contactId, phoneNumber, phoneType, createdAt)
SELECT c.id, '9549462807', 'Mobile', NOW()
FROM contacts c
JOIN properties p ON c.propertyId = p.id
WHERE p.addressLine1 LIKE '%285 Sw 12th%' AND p.city = 'Pompano Beach' AND c.name = 'Charlotte Holland OV'
ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE phoneNumber = VALUES(phoneNumber);

INSERT INTO contactEmails (contactId, email, createdAt)
SELECT c.id, 'dorothyveach@att.net', NOW()
FROM contacts c
JOIN properties p ON c.propertyId = p.id
WHERE p.addressLine1 LIKE '%285 Sw 12th%' AND p.city = 'Pompano Beach' AND c.name = 'Charlotte Holland OV'
ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE email = VALUES(email);
